snippet.textDisplay:
"Find a dark room - somewhere you can be alone. Listen to this with some reasonable quality headphones. Close your eyes. Hear the different layers of music coming and going, concentrate on each instrument as they coalesce and form rhythms and beats that carry you away - sway your head in rhythm with the music and exclude all other thoughts from your mind. Just the music, just the rhythm. Enter into an almost trance-like state with the music totally taking over who you are, everything around you. If you are completely absorbed by the music, maybe you will smile or laugh at just how good this is. This isn't just music - this is a place where you can go, somewhere you can lose yourself and forget your troubles. This is utterly mesmerising. Love it!
😍😍👌👌"
